                    <h3>Challenge 2: Automated Matching</h3>
                    <p><strong>Problem:</strong> Manual matching is slow and subjective</p>
                    <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Optimize for satisfaction and profile similarity</p>
                    <p><strong>Deliverable:</strong> Automated Recommendation Engine</p>
                </div>
                
                <h3>üö® At-Risk Match Indicators</h3>
                <div class="grid">
                    <div class="card" style="border-left-color: #dc3545;">
                        <h4>üî¥ High Risk</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Acceptance delay > 100 days</li>
                            <li>Needs overlap < 0.2</li>
                            <li>Engagement score < 0</li>
                            <li>Field similarity = 0</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="card" style="border-left-color: #ffc107;">
                        <h4>üü° Medium Risk</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Acceptance delay 50-100 days</li>
                            <li>Needs overlap 0.2-0.4</li>
                            <li>Engagement score 0-2</li>
                            <li>Partial field mismatch</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <h3>Intervention Strategies</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>High Acceptance Delay:</strong> Send reminders, escalate to coordinator</li>
                    <li><strong>Low Needs Overlap:</strong> Suggest rematch, provide reasoning</li>
                    <li><strong>Low Engagement:</strong> Send tips, schedule check-ins</li>
                    <li><strong>Field Mismatch:</strong> Highlight cross-domain benefits</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
