            <div id="features" class="tab-content">
                <h2>üîë Key Features for Modeling</h2>
                
                <p>All features are <span class="highlight">human-understandable and interpretable</span></p>
                
                <div class="grid">
                    <div class="grid-item">
                        <h4>1. Needs Overlap Score</h4>
                        <p class="star">‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê</p>
                        <p><strong>Calculation:</strong> Jaccard similarity</p>
                        <p><strong>Why:</strong> Direct alignment = satisfaction</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="grid-item">
                        <h4>2. Field Similarity</h4>
                        <p class="star">‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê</p>
                        <p><strong>Calculation:</strong> Text matching</p>
                        <p><strong>Why:</strong> Domain expertise alignment</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="grid-item">
                        <h4>3. Engagement Score</h4>
                        <p class="star">‚≠ê‚≠ê</p>
                        <p><strong>Source:</strong> Mentee data</p>
                        <p><strong>Why:</strong> Predicts participation</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="grid-item">
                        <h4>4. Acceptance Delay</h4>
                        <p class="star">‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê</p>
                        <p><strong>Calculation:</strong> Days to accept</p>
                        <p><strong>Why:</strong> Strong risk indicator</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="grid-item">
                        <h4>5. Binome Score</h4>
                        <p class="star">‚≠ê‚≠ê</p>
                        <p><strong>Source:</strong> Historical rating (7-9)</p>
                        <p><strong>Why:</strong> Quality metric</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="grid-item">
                        <h4>6. Study Level</h4>
                        <p class="star">‚≠ê</p>
                        <p><strong>Calculation:</strong> Bac+1 to Bac+5+</p>
                        <p><strong>Why:</strong> Experience gap</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card info">
                    <h3>Feature Engineering Example</h3>
                    <pre>
def calculate_needs_overlap(mentor_needs, mentee_needs):
    mentor_set = set(mentor_needs.split(', '))
    mentee_set = set(mentee_needs.split(', '))
    
    overlap = len(mentor_set & mentee_set)
    union = len(mentor_set | mentee_set)
    
    return overlap / union  # Jaccard similarity
                    </pre>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- MODEL TAB -->
            <div id="model" class="tab-content">
                <h2>üìä Model Architecture</h2>
                
                <div class="card info">
                    <h3>Model Choice: Random Forest Classifier</h3>
                    <h4>Why Random Forest?</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>‚úÖ Naturally interpretable (tree-based)</li>
                        <li>‚úÖ Built-in feature importance</li>
                        <li>‚úÖ Handles non-linear relationships</li>
                        <li>‚úÖ Robust to outliers</li>
                        <li>‚úÖ Works with SHAP for explainability</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <h3>Hyperparameters</h3>
                <pre>
n_estimators: 100
max_depth: 10
min_samples_split: 50
class_weight: 'balanced'
random_state: 42
                </pre>
                
